    id: "history-straw-hat-riots-0422",
    title: "The Straw Hat Riots: When New Yorkers Fought Over Fashion in 1922",
    excerpt: "Men wearing straw hats after September 15 risked having their hats stomped — and the tradition led to full-scale riots.",
    category: "History",
